OL,3,CFormer Bristol Rugby captain dies aged
OL,4,C49
OL,6,FPosting on social media, Bristol Bears
OL,7,Fsaid they are "deeply saddened to hear
OL,8,Fof the passing of legendary former
OL,9,Fcaptain"
OL,11,FThey went on to say their thoughts are
OL,12,Fwith his family, friends and everyone
OL,13,Fat Clifton Rugby.
OL,15,FPlymouth Albion described Salter
OL,16,Fcontribution to rugby as 'significant'
OL,17,Fsaying he was "widely respected within
OL,18,Fthe game."
